I"¦<p>Our University admits a large troop of students for undergraduation. And so the hostel booking process becomes difficult (when servers add to the crowd problem). But thatâ€™s totally out of our hands. What this tiny tool could do is host the entire student hostel database when the correct data is inputted by the crowd <em>after hostel booking is over</em>.</p>

<p>The site is currently live at <a href="http://hostelroo.ml/">hostelroo.ml</a>.</p>

